NAS Docker 部署方案（前后端分离：Vue + Spring Boot + MySQL）

一、架构说明

- 三个容器：`nginx`、`backend`、`mysql`
- `nginx`：托管前端 `dist`，并将 `/api` 反向代理到 `backend:8080`
- `backend`：仅内网可见，连接 `mysql:3306`，不暴露公网端口
- `mysql`：仅内网可见，数据持久化到 NAS

二、docker-compose.yml

```yaml
services:
  nginx:
    image: your-registry/navhub-nginx:${NGINX_TAG:-v1}
    build:
      context: ./nginx
      dockerfile: Dockerfile
    container_name: navhub-nginx
    ports:
      - "80:80"
      # 如需 https 可再加：
      # - "443:443"
    volumes:
      # 前端 dist 外置挂载（可直接替换 dist 迭代）
      - /nas/web/dist:/usr/share/nginx/html:ro
      # 如需在 NAS 上覆盖 nginx 配置，可启用下面这行
      # - /nas/nginx/default.conf:/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf:ro
    depends_on:
      - backend
    restart: unless-stopped

  backend:
    image: your-registry/navhub-backend:${BACKEND_TAG:-v1}
    build:
      context: ./backend
      dockerfile: Dockerfile
    container_name: navhub-backend
    expose:
      - "8080" # 仅容器内可见，不对宿主机公网暴露
    environment:
      TZ: Asia/Shanghai
      SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE: prod
      SPRING_CONFIG_ADDITIONAL_LOCATION: /app/config/
      # 也可直接用环境变量覆盖（可选）
      # SPRING_DATASOURCE_URL: jdbc:mysql://mysql:3306/navhub?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=Asia/Shanghai&characterEncoding=utf8
      # SPRING_DATASOURCE_USERNAME: navhub
      # SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD: ${MYSQL_PASSWORD}
      # JAVA_OPTS: -Xms256m -Xmx512m
    volumes:
      - /nas/app/config:/app/config:ro
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
    restart: unless-stopped

  mysql:
    image: mysql:${MYSQL_TAG:-8.0.36}
    container_name: navhub-mysql
    command:
      - --default-authentication-plugin=mysql_native_password
      - --character-set-server=utf8mb4
      - --collation-server=utf8mb4_unicode_ci
    environment:
      TZ: Asia/Shanghai
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: ${MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD}
      MYSQL_DATABASE: ${MYSQL_DATABASE:-navhub}
      MYSQL_USER: ${MYSQL_USER:-navhub}
      MYSQL_PASSWORD: ${MYSQL_PASSWORD}
    volumes:
      - /nas/mysql/data:/var/lib/mysql
      # 可选：外置 mysql 配置
      # - /nas/mysql/conf:/etc/mysql/conf.d:ro
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD-SHELL", "mysqladmin ping -h 127.0.0.1 -u root -p$$MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD --silent"]
      interval: 10s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 10
    restart: unless-stopped
```

三、后端 Dockerfile（Spring Boot）

路径：`backend/Dockerfile`

```dockerfile
# ===== build stage =====
FROM maven:3.9.9-eclipse-temurin-17 AS builder
WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
COPY src ./src
RUN mvn -B -DskipTests clean package

# ===== runtime stage =====
FROM eclipse-temurin:17-jre
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar /app/app.jar

EXPOSE 8080
ENTRYPOINT ["sh", "-c", "java $JAVA_OPTS -jar /app/app.jar"]
```

四、nginx Dockerfile + nginx.conf

路径：`nginx/Dockerfile`

```dockerfile
FROM nginx:1.27-alpine
COPY nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf
```

路径：`nginx/nginx.conf`

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name _;

    root /usr/share/nginx/html;
    index index.html;

    # Vue 静态资源 + history 路由支持
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }

    # 反向代理后端 API
    location /api/ {
        proxy_pass http://backend:8080;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;

        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

        proxy_connect_timeout 5s;
        proxy_read_timeout 60s;
    }
}
```

五、外置后端配置示例

路径：`/nas/app/config/application-prod.yml`

```yaml
server:
  port: 8080

spring:
  datasource:
    url: jdbc:mysql://mysql:3306/navhub?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=Asia/Shanghai&characterEncoding=utf8
    username: navhub
    password: your_db_password
    driver-class-name: com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver

  jpa:
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: update
    show-sql: false
```

六、.env 版本管理示例

路径：`deploy/.env`

```env
# 镜像版本（不要用 latest）
NGINX_TAG=v1
BACKEND_TAG=v1
MYSQL_TAG=8.0.36

MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=ChangeMe_Root_123
MYSQL_DATABASE=navhub
MYSQL_USER=navhub
MYSQL_PASSWORD=ChangeMe_App_123
```

七、最小目录结构

```text
deploy/
├── docker-compose.yml
├── .env
├── nginx/
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   └── nginx.conf
└── backend/
    ├── Dockerfile
    ├── pom.xml
    └── src/...

NAS 外置目录（宿主机）:
├── /nas/mysql/data
├── /nas/app/config
└── /nas/web/dist
```

八、部署 / 升级 / 回滚命令

首次部署：

```bash
docker compose --env-file .env up -d --build
```

升级后端（例如 `v1 -> v2`）：

1) 修改 `.env`：`BACKEND_TAG=v2`
2) 执行：

```bash
docker compose --env-file .env pull backend
docker compose --env-file .env up -d --no-deps backend
```

升级前端（替换 dist）：

```bash
docker compose --env-file .env restart nginx
```

回滚（切回旧版本 tag）：

```bash
docker compose --env-file .env pull backend nginx
docker compose --env-file .env up -d --no-deps backend nginx
```

九、上线注意事项（必须）

- 不要把 `mysql` 配 `ports` 对外暴露
- 不要执行 `docker compose down -v`（会删数据卷）
- MySQL 数据持久化：`/nas/mysql/data -> /var/lib/mysql`
- 后端配置外置：`/nas/app/config -> /app/config`
- 镜像必须用版本号（`v1/v2/v3`），不要用 `latest`

